Overview
The Color Theory Collection allows you to create a unique color story by pairing vibrant, unexpected hues with our iconic footwear silhouettes. Made with sturdy canvas uppers, the Color Theory Authentic honors our original low top, lace-up shoe with eye-catching colorways ideal for the season. This time-honored style also includes metal eyelets and signature rubber waffle outsoles. • Vans’ original low top shoe • Lace-up closure • Sturdy canvas uppers • Metal eyelets • Signature rubber waffle outsoles • 4 metal eyelet lace rows for sizes 3.5-6 • 5 metal eyelet lace rows for sizes 6.5 and up

Customs. Since before that was a thing.

Vans Customs have been a tradition since 1966, when Paul Van Doren made shoes with any fabric people brought by the shop. Today, the creativity is still in your hands. Pick your shoe, pick your colors and patterns, and make them yours.

Delivered to you in 4-6 weeks with free shipping.
